  "texts": [
    "Three TCM doctors conducted independent searches within databases and cross-verified the results during weekly meetings.",
    "If they were unable to reach a consensus on the outcomes during these meetings, a TKM doctor made the final decision to create the TF vocabulary.",
    "By adopting this approach, we successfully constructed a comprehensive TF vocabulary that encompasses the heterogeneous English expressions of TF encountered in scholarly literature.",
    "As an example, the traditional formula 五積散 has been assigned different English transliterations, including ojeok-san, wuji-san, goseki-san, and goshaku-san.",
    "By consolidating these transliterations, we performed a comprehensive search on PubMed to identify relevant articles associated with TF."
